Function reference

A summary

Some functions are merged into R/gap as shown here, https://jinghuazhao.github.io/R/vignettes/gap.html. The following datasets are available as internal objects: biomaRt, caprion, hg19, hg19Tables, inf1, Olink_NGS, Olink_qPCR, SomaLogic160410, st4, s6, swath_ms.
